      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry, what? i didn't mention any goblins. anyway, back to the fabric—if the weave is too tight and it reduces airflow, does that mean we'll see more heat retention in the sheets? i'm worried about customers complaining it feels stuffy in the summer.",
